text: Antwone is an African-American English given name associated with Antoine and Anthony in use in the United States. Notable people with this name include the following people. *Antwone Fisher (born 1959), American director, screenwriter, author, and film produce *Antwone Savage (born 1981), American gridiron football player ==See also== *Antwon (name) *Antwoine ==Notes== Category:African-American given names
title: Antwone
